Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli wata tashar talabijin ta Amurka a ranar Alhamis don sauraron shaidar Brett Kavanaugh, dan takarar Kotun Koli ta Amurka, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin fyade da aka ce ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba yayin da tashoshin watsa labarai suka dakatar da shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don abin mamaki na ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya shirya don bincika tuhumar na mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa ta tabbata da cewa wani mutum mai maye ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya bayyana a cikin shaidar da aka yi cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito sun kalli bidiyon a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Babu wasu bayanai da aka samu nan da nan game da sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka watsa wannan shari'ar, kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana yawan samun matsala wajen kirga yawan mutanen da suke kallon ofishin.
Idan aka gwada, wannan yana kama da wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma bikin Oscar.
Tashar Fox News, wacce ke goyon bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ita ce ta fi yawan masu kallo a ranar sauraron karar, wanda ya kai miliyan 5.69 a matsakaita, a cewar Nielsen.
