Bayan da ofishin shugaban kasar ya bayyana cewa zai goyi bayan Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi da safiya a ranar Juma'a yana ihu yayin da yake kokarin hawa motar hawa zuwa wani taron shari'a.
