An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da masu fafutukar neman 'yancin kai suka yi fada da 'yan sanda a yayin da dubban mutane ke zanga-zangar nuna adawa a ranar farko ta zaben neman 'yancin kai da aka yi a Catalonia wanda ya raba yankin zuwa rukuni biyu.
Wasu 'yan tawaye masu saka kayan kwalliya da 'yan sanda suka dakatar sun harbe jami'an da kwai da kuma fenti mai tururi, wanda hakan ya haifar da duhu a kan titunan da yawanci ke cike da masu yawon bude ido.
