Abubuwan da ke faruwa a duniya da ke nuna cewa akwai wasu ƙasashe da ke da wuyan bi da Amurka, da kuma cewa muna neman sabuwar hanyar da za mu bi wajen samar da fasaha ta wucin gadi,  Lee ya ce.
A ninka kudade zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa babban ci gaban AI na gaba zai faru a Amurka, Lee ya fada a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order aka buga a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin.
A shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin A.I. wanda ya doke mafi kyawun ɗan wasan American Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama manajan a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban sashen China na Google.
Lee ya nuna godiyarsa ga gasar fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ta shirya, kamar Gasar Robotics ta Hukumar Kula da Ayyukan Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba, saboda zai taimaka wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
