"China ba ta karbar manyan malamanmu, kamfanoni ne ke karbar su", in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da kuma wasu kamfanonin fasaha sun ɗauki manyan malamai daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya ce kokarin Amurka kan AI zai amfana daga sauya manufofin shige da fice.
Ya ce, "Ya kamata duk wanda ya kammala karatun digirinsa na kimiyya ya sami green card ta atomatik".
