A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence, wanda aka yi niyyar haɗa abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da masana kimiyya a cikin wannan yunƙurin, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓaɓɓen kan Ilimin Artificial.
