Amma har yanzu ba a san yawan mintuna da zai yi a wasan ba.
"Za a samu fiye da daya, kuma kasa da 48," Walton ya fada a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto game da Lakers Mike Trudell ya ce a cikin wani tweet cewa James zai iya yin wasa na iyakantaccen minti.
Bayan kammala atisayen a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasannin Lakers na wasanni shida kafin kakar wasa.
