Lokacin taron zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump zai fara wani taron gangamin zabe a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin zaben shugaban kasa guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wuraren da yake so, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka dakatar da zaben dan takarar da ya fi so a kan kujerar kotun koli, Trump na son samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a kan majalisar dokoki lokacin da aka kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai fara a daren yau kuma yaya kuke kallon sa a yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, zai fara ne yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe 7 na dare.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon game da mai neman zama babban alkalin kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya kara zama da damuwa yayin da ake zargin Kavanaugh da laifin lalata da kuma majalisar dattijai na iya jira har zuwa mako guda don kada kuri'ar nadin sa yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban manufar wannan jerin gangamin shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman shugabancin kasar a watan Nuwamba su samu karin kuzari.
Shugabannin yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump sun ce gangamin gangamin zabe guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai", kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa, don haka shugaban yana tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron na yau da dare a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling na iya jan hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a tattauna a kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ce.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata guda da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya ragu a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya ba shi goyon baya a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA a shirye take ta yi gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a gasar cin kofin duniya a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi wasanni uku a rana ɗaya, wasannin hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma na iya zama abin da gasar Ryder ta buƙaci.
Rashin daidaituwa na rashin daidaituwa shine ainihin wasan kwaikwayo na wasanni, amma wanda 'yan wasa suka gaskata, musamman ma a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, wane ne ke da zarafi mafi kyau a wannan lokacin?
Da farko suna da maki shida a gaba, yanzu sun kara hudu, don haka muna ganin cewa sa'a tana tare da mu a yanzu, Jordan Spieth ya ce kafin ya bar wurin a ƙarshen rana.
Hakika, Turai tana da fa'ida ta samun maki hudu, yayin da akwai maki 12 a wasa.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa suna da iska a cikin jirgin ruwa, kuma akwai abubuwa da yawa da ke ƙarfafa su, ba a rage ba da yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya zira kwallaye uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai tsoratar da mutane daga tee zuwa green kuma yana kafa misali mai kyau.
Sautin da yake yi a lokacin da yake wasa sosai ya kara daɗaɗa yayin da zagayensa ya ci gaba, kuma ya yi wani muhimmin rami wanda ya sa wasa na huɗu ya zama nasara lokacin da shi da Thomas suka ragu da maki biyu bayan wasanni biyu.
Gidan da ya yi da ya lashe wasan a 15 ya biyo bayan irin wannan ihu, irin wanda za ka iya gane cewa ya yi imanin cewa ba a ci tawagar Amurka ba tukuna.
"Dole ne ka yi zurfin bincike kuma ka damu da wasan ka kawai", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da waɗannan 'yan wasan za su iya yi a yanzu.
Akwai ramuka 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa kawai da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin Ryder Cup da babu shakka.
Wannan rukunin 'yan Turai masu ban mamaki da kuma farin ciki suna da 'yan wasa huɗu da ba za su yi kuskure ba.
Moliwood ita ce kawai ƙungiyar da ba ta buga bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma kuma a ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Jumma'a da safe sun guje wa bogey.
Saboda wannan jerin, da kuma yadda suke nuna ikon musayar makamashi da masu sauraron su, su ne 'yan wasan da za a doke ranar Lahadi.
Zai fi dacewa duka biyu a lokaci guda a ramuka daban-daban.
Amma, ba a san lokacin da za a ce an yi nasara a Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi nasara a kan Sergio Garcia, gwarzon dan wasan kwallon hudu a safiyar ranar, lokacin da ya yi aiki tare da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da kuma biyu doubles a gaban tara ya haifar da raguwa ga Mutanen Espanya da Sweden wanda ba za su iya ci gaba ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka biya kuɗin da kake bukata.
Wasanni huɗu da kuma wasan huɗu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallon ta hanyar hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarar da suke bayarwa, shawarar da ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin ƙiftawar ido.
Kungiyar Turai ta yi wasa sosai kuma tana da kyakkyawan ci gaba a ranar karshe, amma wannan wasan na hudu ya nuna cewa Team USA na shirye don yin gwagwarmaya, wani abu da wasu, musamman a Amurka, suka yi shakkarsa.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai ta fara da kyakkyawan ci a rana ta karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan wasan hudu da hudu da aka yi a ranar Asabar, inda ta ci Amurka da ci 10 da 6.
'Yan wasan biyu Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci tawagarsu da nasara biyu fiye da Tiger Woods, wanda ke fama da wahala, wanda ya sa yanzu suna da maki hudu a Le Golf National.
Kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ke son dawo da kofin da ta rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta fi Amurkawa a wasan hudu da safe, da ci 3-1.
Amurka ta yi tsayayya sosai a gasar hudu, inda ta ci wasanni biyu amma ba ta iya ci gaba da ci gaba ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk za ta samu maki takwas a wasanni 12 na wasan da za a yi a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci gaba da lashe gasar.
Fleetwood ne dan wasa na farko a Turai da ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da Molliwood, bayan karshen mako mai ban sha'awa, sun zama biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da suka ci kwallaye hudu a wasanninsu hudu na farko.
Bayan sun samu Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan hudu, sun yi wasa da juna sosai, sun doke Woods da kuma dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da karfi 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna kyakkyawan motsawa a wasu lokuta, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a cikin hudu-balls da foursomes da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya shirya don wasan hudu na safiyar yau, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu kuma tare suka doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, na daya da uku a duniya, ta 2 & 1.
Duk da haka, ba a yi tafiya a kan tudu mai laushi ba a Turai a wannan rana mai daɗi da iska mai iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar zakarun Amurka sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga Amurkawa a ranar Asabar da maki uku.
Sun ci nasara bayan wani wasa mai wuya tare da 2&1 daga Spain Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin hudu-balls kuma daga bisani suka doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy da 4&3 a cikin foursomes, bayan sun rasa ramuka hudu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta samu nasarar rufe ragamar maki hudu a farkon wasan, duk da cewa tawagar Furyk tana da isasshen damar yin wasa, tun da yake a yanzu suna riƙe da kofin.
Amma yanzu da suka kasance a matsayi na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, wani hari a ranar Lahadi yana da wuya.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta taba yin watsi da makamai ba ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa na kara janyo rashin amincewa a Amurka kuma a karkashin irin wannan yanayi ba za ta iya barin makaman nukiliyarta ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "manyan matakai na kyakkyawar niyya" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman rokoki, rushe wurin gwajin nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin dakatar da yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
Ya ce, "amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba".
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba za mu yi watsi da makamai ba.
Ko da yake Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da adawar Washington da tsarin 'tsara-tsara' na yaduwar nukiliya, inda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da ta ci gaba da yin wasu matakai, ya zama abin lura cewa bai yi watsi da yaduwar nukiliya ba a priori, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa tsakanin Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump a lokacin taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni a Singapore, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "rashin nukiliya na yankin Koriya", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950 zuwa 1953, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kira da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta bukaci dnanukilar farko kuma ta kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa har ma ta yi hamayya da ayyana ƙarshen yaƙi, in ji Ri.
Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya sa mu durƙusa shine gidan iska na mutanen da basu san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da yi yana ƙara sa mu rashin amincewa.
Ri bai bayyana wani shiri na taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wani abu da shugaban Amurka ya gabatar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya jaddada tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan da Koriya ta Kudu ce ta kasance ita ce ta biyu a wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya maimakon Amurka, to, da a ce har yanzu ba a samu irin wannan matsalar ba.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na bara, lokacin da ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa za a harba makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa zuwa Amurka bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "Majin kunar bakin wake" a kan wani aikin kashe kansa.
