Amurka za ta iya amfani da sojan ruwanta wajen kafa wani 'kulle' don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - ministan cikin gida
Washington na iya amfani da sojan ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don hana makamashi na Rasha shiga kasuwa, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Ryan Zinke, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, inda kasar ke aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
