Abin baƙin ciki ne".
Tom Daley ya ji kansa "mai rauni" saboda jima'i
Mai tsalle-tsalle na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce a lokacin ƙuruciyarsa ya ji ya kasa saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya sa ya yi nasara.
Matashin mai shekara ashirin da huɗu ya ce bai fahimci cewa 'ba kowa ba ne kamarsa ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.'
A wata hira da Desert Island Discs a Radio 4 tare da Lauren Laverne, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin' yan luwadi don ba wasu 'bege'.
Ya kuma ce yin renon yara ya sa ya daina mai da hankali ga samun nasara a gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta saba gabatar da wannan shiri mai tsawo, ta ɗauki wasu watanni domin rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin mai lalata a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya gaya masa cewa a lokacin ƙuruciyarsa ya ji "ƙananan" fiye da wasu saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba a cikin zamantakewa don son 'yan mata da yara".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan motsin zuciyarmu, na zama ƙasa da wasu, na zama dabam, su ne ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Yana son ya nuna cewa shi "wani ne" don kada ya ɓata wa mutane rai idan suka san halinsa.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama fitaccen mai fafutukar kare hakkin LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da kasancewarsa a wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Ostiraliya a wannan shekara don yin kira ga wasu ƙasashe da su dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne domin yana farin ciki cewa yana iya yin rayuwa a fili ba tare da wata matsala ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu 'bege.'
Gwarzon gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce gaskiyar cewa ya ƙaunaci wani mutum, mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Back, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013, "ya ba ni mamaki sosai".
Daley ta auri Oscar a bara, wanda ya girme shi da shekara 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da kake da matashi da yawa don jimrewa", ya shiga gasar Olympics ta farko yana da shekaru 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka, yana da wuya a sami wani a cikin shekarunka wanda ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da kuma rashin jin daɗi.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley a watan Yuni, kuma Daley ya ce "dukan ra'ayinsa" ya canja.
"Idan ka yi mini wannan tambayar a bara, da na ce komai ya shafi lashe zinare", in ji shi.
"Amma ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi muhimmanci a duniya fiye da lashe zinare na Olympics.
"Na lashe lambar zinare ta Olympics a matsayin Robbie".
Ɗansa yana da sunan mahaifinsa wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano shi da ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambayi shi shi ne ko sun riga sun samu tikitin zuwa London 2012 domin yana son zama a jere na gaba.
"Ba zan iya samun shi a kan zuciyata in ce, ba za ka kasance a can don zama a kan farko line, baba", ya ce.
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi kuma ba har sai numfashinsa ya tsaya kuma ya mutu ba, zan iya gane cewa ba shi da ƙarfi", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarkin yi a rayuwata, kuma yin iyo a gaban jama'a a lokacin gasar Olympics, ba abin da ya fi wannan farin ciki", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma shine abin da ya sa ya fara yin waƙa, Proud by Heather Small, wanda ya sa ya yi tsalle a kan hanyar zuwa wasan kwaikwayo kuma har yanzu yana jin tsoro.
Za a iya sauraron Desert Island Discs a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 BST.
Mickelson, ba shi da kyau, a kan benci a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi a wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47, amma dole ne ya dawo cikin siffar da ya saba da ita kafin ya zama babban abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ya shiga gasar karo na 12 a shekara biyu, ya kasance babban rikodin, kyaftin din Jim Furyk ya sanya shi a kan benci don wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan kamar yadda ya yi a yawancin lokaci a Amirka, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni biyar ya raba ranar tsakanin tallafa wa abokan aikinsa da kuma yin aiki a filin motsa jiki don ya san abin da ya ɓace.
Tun da yake ba a san shi da kai tsaye ba har ma a lokacin da ya fi ƙwarewa, ɗan shekara 48 ba shi da kyau a ƙwanƙwasa fairways na Le Golf National, inda tsayi mai tsayi na ƙwallon ƙafa ke azabtar da kullun.
Kuma idan tseren da kansa bai isa ya tsoratar da ku ba, Mickelson zai yi wasa a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar Open ta Burtaniya, wanda aka haɗa shi da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe duka wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa da ke da maki hudu a baya a farkon wasannin guda 12 suka fara da kyau, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa yana da bangaskiya ga wannan mutumin, ko da yake gaskiya, ba zai yiwu ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayin da yake da shi a yau, ya bugi baya na, ya rungume ni kuma ya ce zai shirya gobe.
"Yana da tabbaci sosai a kansa.
An saka shi a cikin zauren suna kuma ya taimaka wa waɗannan ƙungiyoyi sosai, a baya, amma har ma a wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tsammanin zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tsammanin za a yi fiye da haka, amma abin da ya faru ke nan, kuma wannan shi ne yadda muka yi tunanin za mu yi.
Yana son ya kasance a wurin kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai iya wuce Nick Faldo a kan yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga.
Hakan na iya nufin ƙarshen wasan Ryder Cup inda bai taɓa yin nasara ba.
Mickelson ya yi nasara a wasanni 18, ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 20, kuma ya ci kwallaye 7, amma Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa a wurin ya yi tasiri sosai a kan tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da hankali, yana son yin dariya tare da mutane kuma yana da babban mutum don samun a cikin tawagar", in ji shi.
