Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din tawagar Turai, ya san cewa babban ci gaba zai iya wucewa cikin sauri
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din tawagar Turai, ya san daga kwarewa cewa, sa'ad da aka fara wasa a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder, da sauƙi, za a iya samun ci gaba a cikin wani yanayi da ba shi da kyau.
Dan Dan Danish din ya fara wasa a Valderrama a 1997, inda tawagar da Seve Ballesteros ya jagoranci ta kasance ta kai maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma a ƙarshe ta wuce layin ƙarshe tare da mafi ƙanƙan iyaka: 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna ci gaba da tuna wa kanku cewa muna da babban ci gaba a Valderrama; muna da babban ci gaba a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma kawai", in ji Bjorn, wanda aka cire a nan, bayan ya ga kungiyar ta 2018 ta ci 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da jiya, yana da kyau ga 10-6 a kan Le Golf National.
Saboda haka tarihi ya nuna min da kuma duk wasu a cikin tawagar cewa wannan ba wasa bane da aka buga.
Za a bukaci kowa ya yi iya ƙoƙarinsa don ya cim ma hakan.
Ka yi aiki, ka yi abin da ya dace.
Ba a gama ba har sai an rubuta maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa guda, kuma ita ce mu lashe wannan kofin, kuma dole ne mu ci gaba da mai da hankali a kan hakan.
Ina ci gaba da cewa, ina mai da hankali ne kan 'yan wasa 12 da muke da su, amma kuma muna sane da mutanen da ke gefen, wasu daga cikin mafi kyawun' yan wasa a duniya. "
Bjorn ya yi farin ciki game da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a kan wani filin golf mai wuya, ya daɗa: "Ba zan taɓa yin tsalle a kan wannan batun ba.
Za mu sake fuskantar wata matsala a gobe.
Za a tattauna game da nasarorin mutum a gobe, kuma wannan wani fanni ne dabam.
Yana da kyau a fita waje tare da abokin tarayya idan abubuwa suna tafiya daidai, amma idan kana tsaye a gabanka, ba a gwada iyawarka a matsayin mai wasan golf ba.
Wannan shi ne saƙon da za ku gaya wa 'yan wasan, ku yi ƙoƙari ku yi mafi kyau a gobe.
Saboda haka, bari abokin aurenku ya yi abin da ya dace kuma ya yi abin da ya dace".
Ba kamar Bjorn ba, abokin hamayyarsa, Jim Furyk, yana tsammanin 'yan wasansa suyi aiki fiye da yadda suke aiki tare.
Furyk da kansa ya sha wahala a fuskar wannan juyin juya halin a ranar ƙarshe, a matsayin memba na ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline da kuma rashin nasara lokacin da Turai ta yi "Miracle of Medina".
"Na tuna da kowace kalma daga wannan jawabin", in ji shi a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din 1999, ya ƙarfafa 'yan wasansa don ranar ƙarshe.
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 da za mu buga gobe, amma bari mu yi ƙoƙari mu fara da kyau, kamar yadda muka yi a Brookline, ko kuma kamar yadda muka yi a Medinah.
Idan muka samu ƙarfin hali, za mu iya matsa wa 'yan wasan da ke tsakiyar filin wasa.
Mun tsara yadda za mu tsara 'yan wasanmu kuma mun tura su a cikin tsari da muka ga ya fi dacewa, kuma za mu yi ƙoƙari mu yi wani abu mai ban mamaki gobe".
Thomas yana da aikin ƙoƙarin jagorantar ƙalubalen, yana sanya Rory McIlroy don wasan farko, kuma Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter sune sauran Turawa a farkon rabin tsarin bugun.
"Na zabi wannan rukuni a wannan tsari, domin ina ganin muna da kullun", in ji Bjorn game da zabinsa na 'yan wasa.
An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin yakin Jamus
An shirya sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwan Jamus da za a fara aiki da shi a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma zai dauki akalla shekara guda kafin a kammala shi saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma hauhawar farashi, kamar yadda kafofin yada labarai na kasar suka ruwaito.
An dage fara aiki da jirgin ruwan 'Rheinland-Pfalz', wanda shi ne babban jirgi a cikin sabon rukunin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ambaton kakakin soja.
An ce jirgin zai shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo bayan isar da shi sun kawo cikas ga wannan shiri mai matukar muhimmanci.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar sojin ruwa ta umarci a shekarar 2007 suna maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
A cewarmu, suna da makamai masu linzami masu yawa, da makamai masu linzami da na'urar kare jiragen ruwa, da kuma wasu fasahohin da ba a iya gani ba, kamar rage radar, infrared da kuma sauti.
Sauran muhimman halaye sune tsawon lokacin kulawa, ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu a jere, nesa da tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, jinkirin da ake yi yana nufin cewa manyan jiragen yaƙi da za su ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje sun riga sun tsufa kafin a soma amfani da su, in ji Die Zeit.
A shekarar da ta gabata, jirgin ruwan F125 ya zama sanannen sanarwa a jaridu lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss da ke Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta tura wani jirgin ruwa zuwa wani mai gina jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san komai ba game da dalilan da suka sa aka mayar da su, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu 'kasawa na software da kayan aiki' da za su sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Kuskuren software sun kasance masu mahimmanci saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg suna aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120, rabin ma'aikatan a kan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana fama da matsanancin nauyi, wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya rage damar da sojojin ke da shi na yin wasu sabbin kayan aiki.
Jirgin ruwan Rhineland-Palatinate yana da nauyin tan 7,000, wanda ya ninka na jiragen ruwa iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da kayan aiki da ke cikin gida, farashin aikin, har da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, yana da matsala.
An ce wannan ya kai dala biliyan 3.1 daga biliyan 2.2 da aka fara.
Matsalolin da sabbin jiragen ruwa ke fuskanta sun kara tsanani saboda gargaɗin da aka yi kwanan nan cewa sojojin Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisa a Jamus ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna da "rashin jiragen ruwa da za su yi aiki".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta yi girma kamar dusar ƙanƙara a tsawon lokaci, domin an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa daga aiki amma ba a kawo wasu ba.
Ya koka cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da za a iya shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
