Ronaldo ya yi watsi da zargin cin zarafinsa yayin da lauyoyinsa ke shirin kai karar wata mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya bayyana zargin cin zarafinsa a matsayin 'labaran karya' kuma ya ce mutane suna 'so su tallata kansu' ta amfani da sunansa.
Lauyoyinsa suna gab da shigar da kara a kan jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta wallafa tuhumar.
Ana zargin dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da laifin cin zarafin wata Ba'amurkiya mai suna Kathryn Mayorga a dakin otel din Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An kuma zarge shi da biyanta dala 375,000 don ta yi shiru game da lamarin, Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
Ta hanyar bidiyo ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 a Instagram Live, Ronaldo, 33, ya kira rahotannin 'labaran karya' sa'o'i kadan bayan da aka ba da rahoton zargin.
"A'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, wannan ba haka ba ne.
Abin da suke faɗa a yau, labaran karya ne", in ji mai lashe kyautar zinare biyar a gaban kyamara.
"Suna son su tallata kansu ta wajen kiran sunana.
Hakan al'ada ne.
Suna son su zama sanannu ta wajen ambata sunana, amma hakan wani ɓangare ne na sana'ar.
Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki, kuma mai kyau a cikinsa" mai wasan kwallon kafa ya kara da cewa, yana murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin gabatar da kara a gaban kotu da nufin gurfanar da Der Spiegel a gaban kotu kan zargin da suka yi na "rubuta rahotanni da ba su dace ba game da sirri", a cewar Reuters.
Lauyan kwallon kafa, Christian Schertz, ya ce dan wasan yana neman diyya don "lalata ta halin kirki a cikin adadin da ya dace da tsananin cin zarafin, wanda wataƙila yana ɗaya daga cikin manyan keta hakkin mutum a cikin 'yan shekarun nan".
An ce an yi zargin ne a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009 a wani dakin hotel na Palms Hotel da Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan sun hadu a wani gidan rawa, Ronaldo da Mayorga sun koma dakin dan wasan, inda ake zargin ya yi mata fyade ta bayan gida, kamar yadda ake cewa a cikin karar da aka shigar a kotun gundumar Clark County a Nevada.
Mayorga ta ce Ronaldo ya durƙusa bayan abin da ya faru kuma ya gaya mata cewa shi "mutumin kirki ne" a kashi 99 cikin ɗari, amma wani lokacin ana watsi da shi a kashi ɗaya cikin ɗari.
Takardun sun ce Ronaldo ya tabbatar da cewa ma'auratan sun yi jima'i, amma sun amince da juna.
Mayorga ta kuma ce ta je wurin 'yan sanda kuma an dauki hotunan raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga baya ta amince da yarjejeniyar waje da kotu saboda tana "tsoron sakamako" da kuma damuwa game da "ta'aziyyar jama'a".
Yanzu mai shekara 34 ta ce tana son a soke yarjejeniyar saboda ta ci gaba da jin rauni daga abin da aka ce ya faru.
Ronaldo ya kusa komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United a lokacin da ake zargin an yi masa fyade kuma ya koma Juventus a watan Agusta a yarjejeniyar da ta kai Yuro miliyan 100.
Brexit: Birtaniya za ta ci gaba da nadamar ficewar masana'antun mota
Birtaniya za ta "daina nadama" idan ta rasa matsayinta na jagorar masana'antar kera motoci a duniya bayan Brexit, in ji Greg Clark, ministan harkokin tattalin arziki.
Ya kara da cewa "abin damuwa" ne Toyota UK ta shaida wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba, kamfanin zai dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a masana'antarsa da ke Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
Clark ya ce, "Muna bukatar yarjejeniya".
Kamfanin kera motoci na Japan ya ce tasirin jinkiri a kan iyakar idan aka yi Brexit ba tare da yarjejeniya ba zai jawo asarar ayyukan yi.
Kamfanin Burnaston, inda ake kera motocin Toyota Auris da Avensis, ya samar da motoci kusan 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata, kuma kashi 90 cikin dari na motocin da aka fitar zuwa wasu kasashen Tarayyar Turai.
"Hakika ra'ayina shi ne idan Birtaniya ta fice daga EU a karshen watan Maris, za mu ga samar da kayayyaki a masana'antarmu ta tsaya cik", in ji Marvin Cooke, manajan daraktan kamfanin Toyota da ke Burnaston.
Wasu kamfanonin kera motoci a Birtaniya, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover, sun kuma nuna damuwarsu game da tasirin ficewar EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba kan yadda cinikin kan iyaka ke aiki.
Alal misali, BMW ta riga ta sanar cewa za ta rufe masana'antar Mini a Oxford na wata guda bayan Brexit.
Masu kera motoci sun fi damuwa da hadarin da ke tattare da samar da kayayyaki idan aka bar kasar ta Birtaniya ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba.
Toyota tana aiki ne a kan tsarin 'just-in-time' inda kowane minti 37 kayayyakin gyara ke zuwa daga masu samar da motoci a Birtaniya da EU.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga watan Maris, za a iya samun tashin hankali a kan iyakoki wanda masana'antu ke ganin zai haifar da jinkiri da karancin sassa.
Toyota ba za ta iya ajiye kayayyaki fiye da kwana ɗaya a tashar ta Derbyshire ba, in ji kamfanin, saboda haka za a dakatar da samarwa.
Clark ya ce shirin Chequers na Theresa May game da dangantakar ta gaba da EU "yana da kyau don kauce wa waɗannan dubawa a kan iyaka".
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya.Muna son samun mafi kyawun yarjejeniya, wanda zai ba mu damar ci gaba da nasarar da muke samu yanzu, amma kuma mu ci gaba da amfani da wannan damar", in ji shi ga masu sauraron shirin BBC Radio 4 na yau.
"Hakika, ba kawai daga Toyota ba amma daga wasu masana'antun, muna bukatar mu ci gaba da wannan tsarin samar da kayayyaki mai nasara".
Toyota ba ta iya cewa tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samarwa ba, amma ta yi gargadin cewa a cikin dogon lokaci, ƙarin farashin zai shafi matsayin kamfanin na gasa kuma hakan zai kawo asarar ayyuka.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston na shekara 24, kuma wanda yake wakiltar ƙungiyar Unite a wurin, ya ce 'yan'uwansa suna ƙara damuwa: "A cikin gogewata, idan an rasa waɗannan ayyukan, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
Wani kakakin gwamnati ya ce: "Mun gabatar da tabbataccen tsari mai inganci don dangantakarmu ta gaba da EU".
Za a iya jinkirta ganawar Trump da Rosenstein, in ji fadar White House
Ana iya "daina" wani taro mai muhimmanci tsakanin Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein har tsawon mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da fafatawa kan wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin Amurka, Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da ayyukan mai gabatar da kara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tasirin Rasha a zaben, alakar da ke tsakanin mataimakan Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban kasa shiga shari'a.
Tambayar ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar, kuma hakan ya sanya 'yancin Mueller cikin hadari, ya ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin jita-jita a Washington har tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya makirufo don rikodin tattaunawa da Trump da kuma kawar da shugaban ta hanyar Amincewa da Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, sa'ad da ya je fadar White House, an yi ta jita-jita cewa yana gab da yin murabus.
Maimakon haka, an sanar da ganawa da Trump, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce zai fi so ya kori Rosenstein, amma sai aka sauya zaman domin kauce wa rikici da sauraron sauraron shari'ar majalisar dattijai, inda Kavanaugh da kuma wata mata da ta zarge shi da lalata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, za su shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya umarci FBI da ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya sake jinkirta kuri'ar a majalisar dattijai.
A ranar Lahadi, Sarah Sanders, shugabar fadar shugaban kasa ta bayyana a Fox News.
Da aka tambaye ta game da taron da Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an kafa kwanan wata ba, zai iya zama a wannan makon, amma kuma za a iya jinkirta shi har na mako guda, saboda duk wasu abubuwa da ke faruwa a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu gani kuma ina son in ci gaba da sanar da manema labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida sun damu da wannan ikirarin: Sanders bai yi taron manema labarai a fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai watsa shiri Chris Wallace ya tambaye ta dalilin da ya sa ta yi hakan.
Sanders ta ce rashin taron manema labarai ba saboda ƙin 'yan jaridar talabijin da ke jan hankalin ba ne, kodayake, ta kara da cewa: "Ba zan musanta cewa suna kokarin jan hankali ba".
Ta kuma ce za a kara samun hulda kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
"Shugaban kasa ya fi kowa yin tambayoyi da amsoshi", in ji ta, ba tare da ta ba da hujja ba. "Mun duba alkaluman".
Za a ci gaba da gudanar da taron manema labarai, in ji Sanders, amma "idan 'yan jarida sun sami damar yin tambayoyi ga shugaban Amurka kai tsaye, hakan ya fi kyau fiye da magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai kuma kun ga mun yi hakan sau da yawa a cikin 'yan makonnin nan kuma hakan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai lokacin da za ku iya magana da shugaban Amurka".
Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a kai a kai lokacin da ya bar Fadar White House ko kuma lokacin da ya halarci zaman jama'a ko taron manema labarai tare da manyan baƙi.
Taron manema labarai da shugaban kasa kadai ke yi ba safai ake yin sa ba.
A birnin New York a wannan makon shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa, ya yi wani bayyanar da ba ta da gaskiya kuma a wasu lokatai abin mamaki ga 'yan jarida da suka taru.
Ministan lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan NHS Scotland daga wasu kasashen EU wasiƙa kan batun Brexit
Ministan lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU da ke aiki a NHS Scotland wasiƙa don nuna godiyar ƙasar da kuma fatan su ci gaba da aiki a NHS bayan Brexit.
Jeane Freeman, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta tura wasika da ke cewa akwai kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta amince ta biya kudin neman zama na dindindin ga 'yan EU da ke aiki a ma'aikatar gwamnati.
A cikin wasikar ta, Freeman ta rubuta: "A lokacin bazara, tattaunawar tsakanin Birtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, kuma za a yanke shawarar da ake tsammani a wannan kaka.
Amma a lokaci guda gwamnatin Birtaniya ta kara tsaurara matakan da za ta dauka na fuskantar yiwuwar rashin cimma yarjejeniya.
Na san cewa waɗannan lokatai ne na rashin tabbas a gare ku duka.
Saboda haka, ina so in sake nanata yadda na yaba wa aikin da dukan ma'aikatan suka yi, ko da wane ƙasa ne su.
Abokan aiki daga ko'ina cikin EU da kuma bayan, suna kawo kwarewa da ƙwarewa masu mahimmanci waɗanda ke ƙarfafawa da haɓaka ayyukan NHS kuma suna ba da fa'idodi ga marasa lafiya da al'ummomin da muke bauta wa.
Hakika, ƙasar Scotland ita ce gidanku, kuma muna son ku zauna a nan".
Christion Abercrombie ya sha jinya bayan ya ji rauni a kai
Dan wasan baya na kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Tennessee State Tigers, Christion Abercrombie, ya sha jinya da gaggawa jiya bayan da ya samu rauni a kansa a wasan da suka yi da Vanderbilt Commodores da suka ci 31-27, Mike Organ na Tennessean ya ruwaito.
Rod Reed, kocin Tennessee State, ya shaida wa manema labarai cewa hatsarin ya faru ne jim kadan kafin a yi hutu.
"Ya zo kan iyakar kuma ya fadi a can", in ji Reed.
Masu koyar da shi da kuma likitoci sun ba shi iskar oxygen a kan layi kafin su kwantar da shi a kan gado kuma su kai shi don ƙarin bincike.
Wani jami'in jihar Tennessee ya shaida wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee cewa Abercrombie ya fito daga dakin aiki a Cibiyar Kiwon Lafiya ta Vanderbilt.
Harris ya kara da cewa "ba a san cikakken bayani game da irin/girman raunin ba" kuma jihar Tennessee na kokarin gano lokacin da raunin ya faru.
Abercrombie, wanda ya fara shiga makarantar sakandare a shekararsa ta biyu, yana cikin shekararsa ta farko a jihar Tennessee bayan da aka tura shi daga Illinois.
An yi masa duka sau biyar a ranar Asabar kafin ya bar filin wasa, wanda ya sa ya yi duka sau 18 a wannan kakar.
