Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a ta kashe, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai ci gaba da karuwa.
Saboda katse hanyoyin sadarwa, hukumomin gwamnati ba su samu wani bayani ba daga yankin Donggala, wanda ke arewacin Palu kuma ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar da ta kai 7.5 a sikelin Richter.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Celebes ne kuma yana kan ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Celebes, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da tsunami ya auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Celebes.
Gwamnatin, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, a cikin 2017 an kiyasta yawan jama'a 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Celebes, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, ma'adinan nickel suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma mafi yawansu suna cikin Morowali, a gefen tekun da ke kusa da Celebes.
A cikin shekaru dari da suka gabata, tsunamis sun yi wa Palu da Donggala barazana a kai a kai, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma yawan girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa a wurin.
Ga jerin wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi muni da aka yi a shekarun baya:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a duk gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe mutane da yawa a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 a sikelin Richter ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta haddasa tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a sikelin Richter ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 a sikelin Richter ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar tekun Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa da ba ta da zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie da ke Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekarar 2004.
Amma ba a sami tsunami ba a wannan karon, amma mutane sama da 100 sun mutu sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa da dama ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na kasar Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin ruwa na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan Sarah Palin, tsohuwar gwamnan Alaska kuma mai neman mataimakin shugaban kasa, an kama shi ne bisa zargin cin zarafin mata.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata, da hana rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma adawa da hukuncin kisa, a cewar rahoton da jami'an 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa, lokacin da wata mace da ya sani ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don yin rahoton laifin da ake zargi, ya kwace wayar ta.
An tsare Palin a gidan yarin Mat-Su a kan belin dala 500, KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar kuma ya bayyana kansa "ba shi da laifi, tabbas" lokacin da aka tambaye shi, in ji cibiyar.
Ana tuhumar Palin da laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin za a iya yanke masa hukuncin daurin shekara guda a gidan yari da kuma tara har zuwa dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake iya yankewa da hukuncin daurin rana guda a gidan yari da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Ba wannan ne karon farko da aka tuhumi Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na shekarar 2017, an zarge shi da cin zarafin mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su ba da rahoton zargin cin zarafin.
Yanzu haka, wannan shari'ar tana gaban kotun sojin Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin gida, da kutsawa cikin rahoton tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makami a cikin abin da ya shafi lamarin.
Abokinsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
A shekara ta 2016, wata kungiyar tsoffin sojoji ta soki Sarah Palin bayan da ta danganta halin tashin hankalin danta da PTSD, wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa a lokacin aikinsa a Iraki.
Indonesia, girgizar ƙasa, tsunami: Daruruwan mutane sun mutu
