Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun bukaci a yankewa Sajfoello Sajpov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar tun 1953.
A cewar tuhumar, Sajpov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da wata motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawa keke da suka shiga hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Sajpov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a cikin gundumar New York.
A cewar takardar da aka gabatar a kotu, za a iya yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta amince da tuhumar da ake yi wa mutane 22 da laifin, ciki har da laifin kisan kai guda takwas don cin zarafin mutane, wanda ake amfani da shi a matsayin laifin aikata laifuka, da kuma laifin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "tsari da shiri sosai" kuma sun bayyana yadda Sajpov ya kai harin a matsayin "mummunan, mummunan aiki da lalata".
"Sajfoello Habiboellajevich Sajpov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni da asara da asarar dukiya", in ji sanarwar.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun fito ne daga kasar Argentina.
Fiye da shekaru goma da suka shige, an yi shari'ar neman hukuncin kisa a Kudancin New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi amma an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa a wani shari'a da aka yi a birnin New York, an kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka gabata a kan zargin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa biyu ta hanyar kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Sajpov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna wani juyayi ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya sanar da masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi, har ma da 'yan sanda.
Sajpov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi don kai harin bayan kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar karar.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin sa a asibitin, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhumar da ake masa da laifin aikata laifuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Sajpov ya ce "bacin rai ne" game da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin a madadin hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara wa duk wadanda abin ya shafa rauni ne", in ji Patton.
A baya, masu kare Sajpov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisa sun ce ya kamata Nigel Farage ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "tallafawa sojojin jama'a" a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron jam'iyyar Conservative.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su ji zafin' 'yan gurguzu, yayin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Mai goyon bayan jam'iyyar Conservative Peter Bone ya shaida wa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta "tafi" da a ce Farage ne ministan Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta bangarorin da suka rabu sosai, an nuna shi ne da 'yan majalisa biyu masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a Birtaniya da ke halartar wani taron zanga-zangar Brexit a birnin.
Firaministan kasar na fama da ci gaba da aiwatar da yarjejeniyar Chequers a yayin da masu goyon bayan ficewa daga EU da masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a EU ke kai mata hari.
Magoya bayanta sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin kulla yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da cikas, ta yadda za ta tilasta wa masu shakkar kudin Turai da 'yan Labour su zabi tsakanin kayan ta da 'hargitsi'.
Bone ya ce a wani taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana so ya "jefar da Chequers a cikin kwandon shara".
Ya ce ya kamata a ba Farage mukaminsa na jarumi kuma ya zama shugaban tattaunawar da za a yi da Brussels.
Bone ya ce, "Idan ya bar aikin, da mun riga mun fita daga aiki".
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu jefa Chequers a cikin kwandon shara".
Don bayyana adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe biyu na duniya don zama masu rauni ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu".
Bone ya yi watsi da duk wata da'awar cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya sauya tun bayan zaben raba gardama na 2016: "Gaskiyar cewa mutanen Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU ba gaskiya ba ce".
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma ta halarci gangamin, inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa kawai: Firaminista, ka saurari mutane.
Chequers ba shi da kyau a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba sa son kuri'u, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan gwagwarmayarmu da ke zuwa gida-gida don tabbatar da cewa an zabe mu.
Ka bar "Chequers" ka saurara".
A wata sanarwa da ta aikawa May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna rike da ayyukansu idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Farage ya shaida wa taron cewa 'yan siyasa suna bukatar su ji zafin da ake yi musu idan suna son su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan yanzu batun amana ne tsakaninmu, mutane, da kuma tsarin siyasarmu", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma mun hallara a yau domin mu gaya musu ba za mu bar ku ku fita ba".
A wani sako da ya aika wa jama'ar da suka yi farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku kunna wutar da ke kan wuta don ku kashe 'yan siyasarmu da ke gab da cin amanar Brexit.
Muna tattara sojojin kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a kuri'ar raba gardamar ficewar Birtaniya daga kungiyar EU, kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun koma Birtaniya mai cin gashin kanta, mai cin gashin kanta da kuma alfahari".
A halin yanzu, masu ci gaba da zama a Birmingham sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kuma sun kammala wannan tafiya tare da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi ta ɗaga tutar da ke ɗauke da rubutun Tories Against Brexit bayan kafa wannan ƙungiyar a ƙarshen mako.
Lord Adonis, dan majalisa na Labour, ya yi ba'a game da matsalolin tsaro na wata manhajar jam'iyyar Conservative a farkon taron su.
"Waɗannan su ne mutanen da ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samar da tsarin IT da duk fasahar Canada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da alaƙa, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu wani abu da ake kira Brexit mai kyau", in ji shi.
Warren ya yi shirin "tunani sosai" game da neman shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa, 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat daga Massachusetts ta bayyana makomar ta a wani taro da aka yi a wani babban birnin yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ke yawan sukar shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman sake zabensa a watan Nuwamba da Geoff Diehl, dan majalisar wakilai na Republican wanda ya jagoranci yakin neman zaben Trump a Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
Ta kasance cibiyar jita-jita cewa tana iya yin gwagwarmaya da Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne na 36 da ta gana da masu jefa kuri'a a wani babban birnin kasar tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani da ke wurin ya tambaye ta ko za ta yi takarar shugaban kasa.
