Gasar 'yan wasa ta Elite: Dundee Stars da Belfast Giants: 5-3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a raga a wasan da Giants ta yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun rama rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants a ranar Juma'a ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka buga a Dundee a ranar Asabar da ta gabata da ci 5 da 3.
Giants sun ci gaba da zira kwallaye biyu a raga a raga daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun ja ragamar gida a gefe, kafin Dwyer ya sake jan ragamar Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya yi daidai da Dundee, kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar da nasara tare da kwallaye biyu.
Wannan ne karo na uku da suka sha kashi a gasar Elite League a wannan kakar wasan da Adam Keefe ya jagoranci, inda suka ci gaba da buga wasan da suka yi a ranar Juma'a da yamma, inda suka doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast.
Wannan ne karo na hudu a wannan kakar da kungiyoyin biyu suka hadu, inda Giants suka lashe wasannin uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara wasan da karfe 3:35 na minti na hudu, wanda ya samu daga Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya ba da kyautar da ta ninka Beauvillier ta kai ta minti hudu bayan haka.
A cikin wani lokaci mai cike da damuwa, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a cikin wasa a 13:10, kafin Matt Marquardt ya ci gaba da daidaita Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya sa Giants suka ci gaba da cin nasara a hutun farko, lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a daren a ƙarshen zangon farko.
'Yan wasan gida sun sake dawowa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaita su tare da burin wasan wuta a 27:37.
Daga nan sai Cownie da Charles Corcoran suka hada kai sosai don taimakawa Nielsen ya jagoranci Dundee a karon farko a wasan, a ƙarshen zangon biyu.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su kara da Milton Keynes a gida a wasansu na gaba ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu a lokacin da yake sa mutane da yawa su tsere daga girgizar ƙasa a cikin jirgin sama
An girmama wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a ƙasar Indonesia a matsayin gwarzo bayan ya mutu don ya taimaka wa jirgin sama da ke ɗauke da ɗarurruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya.
Mutane sama da 800 ne suka mutu, wasu kuma da dama sun bace bayan wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Celebes a ranar Juma'a, wanda daga bisani ya haifar da tsunami.
Har yanzu ana fama da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun binne a ƙarƙashin dutsen a garin Palu.
Duk da cewa abokan aikinsa suna gudu don ceton rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, dan shekara 21, ya ki barin mukaminsa a cikin hasumiyar zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ta Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport Palu.
Ya zauna don ya tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air mai lamba 6321 wanda ke kan hanya a lokacin ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga kan tashar jirgin sama, sa'ad da yake ganin cewa za ta rushe.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Yohannes Sirait, mai magana da yawun kamfanin Air Navigation Indonesia, ya ce shawarar da ya yanke na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, ABC News ta ruwaito daga Australia.
Mun shirya wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan don ya kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici, mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
"Yana karya zuciyarka idan ka ji hakan", in ji shi.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai, kuma sun sanar da hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasar cewa an hana shiga garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Ana ganin yawan mutanen da suka mutu na ci gaba da ƙaruwa saboda akwai gawawwaki da yawa da ke cikin tarkace da ba a kai ga inda suka mutu ba", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar.
Raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita shida sun lalata Palu, inda za a yi jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "Ana kawo gawawwaki a cikin motar asibiti kowane minti.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da wuya.
Ana yin fashi a dukan wuraren sayar da abinci".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta Indonesiya tana cikin tseren neman taimako ga wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Wannan bala'i ne yanzu, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban kasar Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi, kuma ya gaya wa sojojin da ke wurin cewa: "Ina kira ga dukkanku da ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk ayyukan da ake bukata don kwashe mutane.
Kuna shirye?" CNN ta ruwaito.
